dct_title_s: To Her most excellent Majesty Queen Victoria this hydrographical map of the British Isles, exhibiting the geographical distribution of the inland waters
dct_description_sm: In upper margin: Petermann's maps of the British Empire: physical geography. Includes: Diagram showing the comparative fall of the principal rivers of the British Isles.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the author by Wm. S. Orr, 147, Strand, July 1849.
